data.description: Welcome to your dream home in a serene cul-de-sac setting! This 5-bedroom, 3-bath residence has been thoughtfully updated to provide you with the utmost comfort and convenience. With its fresh interior paint, new carpet, and sleek laminate wood flooring, central AC, the home offers a modern and inviting atmosphere from the moment you step inside.    The exterior of the home boasts newer paint and a well-maintained roof, ensuring that its curb appeal is second to none. As you enter the main living area, you'll be greeted by a kitchen that is perfect for the aspiring chef and a separate dining room that leads to a huge deck. Enjoy the perfect blend of indoor-outdoor living as you entertain guests or simply relax amidst the tranquil surroundings.    The living room is a true highlight, generously illuminated with natural light that creates a warm and inviting ambiance. On the main level, you'll find three bedrooms, each offering comfort and charm, along with an updated bath featuring custom tile work.    The master retreat is a private oasis, complete with its own updated bath featuring exquisite custom tile, providing you with the perfect space to unwind after a long day. You'll wake up each morning feeling refreshed and rejuvenated.    The lower level of the home is a haven for relaxation and entertainment, with a large family room anchored by a cozy wood-burning fireplace. Additionally, two more bedrooms and another well-appointed bath make this level perfect for extended family or guests.    This lower level also boasts a walkout to the backyard. The bonus room offers versatility, making it ideal for an office, exercise room, hobby space, or extra storage to suit your unique needs.    Conveniently located near shopping centers, schools, Fort Carson along with easy access to I-25 for seamless connectivity to the broader community.    Don't miss the opportunity to make it yours and enjoy your home in this desirable location!
